### User Endpoints Testing File

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@registerEmail = test@example.com
@registerPassword = Password123456
@registerName = John
@registerLastName = Doe
@registerNif = 12345678A
@authToken = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE

---

## AUTHENTICATION (No requieren JWT)

### 1. Registrarse - POST /api/user/register
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{registerEmail}}",
  "password": "{{registerPassword}}",
  "name": "{{registerName}}",
  "lastName": "{{registerLastName}}",
  "nif": "{{registerNif}}",
  "role": "admin"
}

### 2. Login - POST /api/user/login
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{registerEmail}}",
  "password": "{{registerPassword}}"
}

### 3. Validar Email con código - PUT /api/user/validation
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/validation
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "123456"
}

### 4. Refrescar token - POST /api/user/refresh
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 5. Logout - POST /api/user/logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/logout
Authorization: {{authToken}}

---

## USER PROFILE (Requieren JWT)

### 6. Obtener usuario autenticado - GET /api/user
GET {{baseUrl}}/user
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 7. Actualizar datos personales - PUT /api/user/register
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/register
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "nif": "12345678A"
}

### 8. Asignar/actualizar compañía - PATCH /api/user/company
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/user/company
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mi Empresa S.L.",
  "cif": "A12345678",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Principal",
    "number": "42",
    "postal": "28001",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  },
  "isFreelance": false
}

### 9. Subir logo de compañía - PATCH /api/user/logo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/user/logo
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="logo"; filename="logo.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./uploads/logo.png
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 10. Cambiar contraseña - POST /api/user/change-password
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/change-password
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "{{registerPassword}}",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123456"
}

### 11. Eliminar usuario - DELETE /api/user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 12. Listar usuarios (admin) - GET /api/user/list
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/list?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 13. Obtener usuario por ID - GET /api/user/:id
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: {{authToken}}
